    "First Launch Tips" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "首次串流提示"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "首次啟動提示"
          }
        },
        "zh-HK" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "首次啟動提示"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "firstLaunchTip" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\n1. By default, The widget menu button will be automatically docked to bottom edge, then become almost transparent after staying idle for 10 seconds. \nThis timeout can be changed by entering “Edit” in the widget menu.\n\n2. From %@ edge, slide %d%% screen width to open settings menu\n\n3. From %@ edge, slide %d%% screen width to open toolbox menu\n\n4. Slide from top 40%% of screen edge to avoid sending touch events to PC side\n\nIf the screen shows large green or purple color artifacts, disable variable display refresh rate on the PC and set the display refresh rate to match the streaming frame rate."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\n1. 默认状态下，控件菜单按键在闲置10秒后将自动吸附屏幕底部边缘，并进入高透明状态。\n可展开控件菜单，进入“修改布局”修改该延迟。\n\n2. 展开设置菜单: 从%@边缘滑动%d%%屏幕宽度\n\n3. 展开工具箱菜单: 从%@边缘滑动%d%%屏幕宽度\n\n4. 从40%%上半边缘滑动避免触控事件影响PC端\n\n若画面出现大片发绿、发紫的颜色异常，请在主机端关闭可变显示刷新率，并将显示刷新率设定为与串流帧率一致。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "\n1. 預設狀態下，控件選單按鍵在閒置10秒後將自動吸附至螢幕底部邊緣，並進入高透明狀態。\n可展開控件選單，進入「修改佈局」修改該延遲。\n\n2. 展開設定選單: 從%@邊緣滑動%d%%螢幕寬度\n\n3. 展開工具箱選單: 從%@邊緣滑動%d%%螢幕寬度\n\n4. 從40%%上半邊緣滑動避免觸控事件影響PC端\n\n若畫面出現大片發綠、發紫等色彩異常，請在主機端關閉可變顯示更新率，並將顯示更新率設定為與串流幀率一致。"
          }
        },
        "zh-HK" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "\n1. 預設狀態下，控件選單按鍵在閒置10秒後將自動吸附至螢幕底部邊緣，並進入高透明狀態。\n可展開控件選單，進入「修改佈局」修改該延遲。\n\n2. 展開設定選單: 從%@邊緣滑動%d%%螢幕寬度\n\n3. 展開工具箱選單: 從%@邊緣滑動%d%%螢幕寬度\n\n4. 從40%%上半邊緣滑動避免觸控事件影響PC端\n\n若畫面出現大片發綠、發紫等色彩異常，請在主機端關閉可變顯示更新率，並將顯示更新率設定為與串流幀率一致。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "firstPressureCurvePersistTip" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Pressure curve saved with current game profile. To switch game profile, tap the [gamepad icon] on navigation bar.\nWhen you switch game profile, pressure curve will change too."
